Package: org.codehaus.groovy.grails.orm.hibernate.query

[Java] Class AbstractHibernateCriteriaBuilder

      • org.codehaus.groovy.grails.orm.hibernate.query.AbstractHibernateCriteriaBuilder
      • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
        Criteria, ProjectionList

        public abstract class AbstractHibernateCriteriaBuilder
extends GroovyObjectSupport

        Abstract super class for sharing code between Hibernate 3 and 4 implementations of HibernateCriteriaBuilder

        Authors:
        Graeme Rocher
        Since:
        3.0.7

        • Nested Class Summary

            Nested classes 
            Modifiers Name Description
            protected class  AbstractHibernateCriteriaBuilder.LogicalExpression instances of this class are pushed onto the logicalExpressionStack to represent all the unfinished "and", "or", and "not" expressions.

          • public Criteria createAlias(String associationPath, String alias)

            Join an association, assigning an alias to the joined association.

            Functionally equivalent to createAlias(String, String, int) using CriteriaSpecificationINNER_JOIN for the joinType.

            throws:
            HibernateException Indicates a problem creating the sub criteria
            Parameters:
            associationPath - A dot-seperated property path
            alias - The alias to assign to the joined association (for later reference).
            Returns:
            this (for method chaining) #see createAlias(String, String, int)

          • public Criteria createAlias(String associationPath, String alias, int joinType)

            Join an association using the specified join-type, assigning an alias to the joined association.

            The joinType is expected to be one of CriteriaSpecification.INNER_JOIN (the default), CriteriaSpecificationFULL_JOIN, or CriteriaSpecificationLEFT_JOIN.

            throws:
            org.hibernate.HibernateException Indicates a problem creating the sub criteria
            Parameters:
            associationPath - A dot-seperated property path
            alias - The alias to assign to the joined association (for later reference).
            joinType - The type of join to use.
            Returns:
            this (for method chaining)
